  "intent": "Execute a Zymo Quick-DNA/RNA viral extraction protocol for 1-6 samples using magnetic bead purification. Add 4\u00b5L proteinase K per well, then 800\u00b5L viral lysis buffer with magnetic beads. Perform magnetic separation followed by sequential wash steps with wash buffer 1, wash buffer 2, and two ethanol washes (500\u00b5L each). Air dry beads for 12 minutes total, then elute nucleic acids in 60\u00b5L nuclease-free water with 10-minute room temperature incubation. Transfer final eluate to clean PCR plate.",
